tone-generator (0.1.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Set indicator and notification tone volumes to 40% (Fixes: NB#118879).
  * Added support for stream-specific volume scaling from the command line.
  * Tag also non-DTMF tones with call volume control properties.
  * Replaced hardcoded stream properties with appropriate command line options.

 -- Krisztian Litkey <krisztian.litkey@nokia.com>  Mon, 14 Sep 2009 18:34:40 +0300

